  "title": "Class 3/4 Lorry Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Drive Class 3 / Class 4 vehicles safely and responsibly</li><li>Deliver and unload products to customers’ premises</li><li>Ensure goods are properly loaded, secured, and unloaded</li><li>Complete delivery orders, delivery notes, and related documentation</li><li>Conduct all deliveries to customers in a safe and service orientated manner</li><li>Follow traffic laws, company SOPs, and safety regulations</li><li>Any other duties assigned by the supervisor</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Possess a Singapore Class 3/4 driving license</p></li><li><p>At least 1 year of driving experience</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-oriented</p></li><li><p>Able to work on weekends or public holidays</p></li><li><p>6 days work week</p></li><li><p>All genders are welcome</p></li><li><p>Preferrably Singaporeans candidate only</p></li></ul>",
